document_title: Whitmore disease (bacterial infection): Causes, symptoms, prevention
subsection_content:
Whitmore through its stages will have a significant impact on the organs in the body. The most common complications in Whitmore patients are:
Skin ulcers; Abscesses (on the skin and organs such as liver, lungs, spleen...); Pneumonia; Sepsis; Meningitis; Dead
